# --- Personal / real data ---
# Convention for this repo: any file ending in "_private.csv" is assumed
# to contain your real personal data (e.g. an actual savings diary) and
# should never be committed. Example/template data files should instead
# be named "*_example.csv" and ARE meant to be tracked.
*_private.csv
*_private.json
